Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The tool I discarded became Gilbert's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.90,0:00:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But after losing both of her arms,\Nher master,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything else in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,there she was,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,standing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.13,0:01:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.06,0:01:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.15,0:01:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You might have made it\Nif you killed me quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:01:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull the emergency brake! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not working!\NTry the brake in the guest car!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull the emergency brakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.01,0:02:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Get the other bomb!\N-I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.73,0:03:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,GARDARIK EMPIRE\NCAPITAL CITY OF HORMGARD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,LEIDENSCHAFTLICH\NINTERIM EMBASSY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.64,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The two nations of Gardarik\Nand Leidenschaftlich
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,hereby recognize each other\Nas equal sovereigns
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to maintain\Nglobal peace and safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To that end,\Nboth nations will resume fair trade,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and Leidenschaftlich shall provide\None year of emergency aid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,as a show of goodwill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We vow to honor this peace treaty\Nbetween our nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-The war is over.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's over...\NEven though the war is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,my son hasn't returned home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told my wife\Nthat we should give up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you write this in the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you for being born our son."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,An air show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't have any during the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is looking forward\Nto our first one in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the deadline.\NSo, it's one more day of hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've been thinking\Nabout writing a letter myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a dancer before I became a Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Many soldiers came to where I worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So many of them lost their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd write a letter to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you write one, too, Violet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have never written a letter\Nof my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it will be your very first one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just write how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I no longer needed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.13,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After I am dismissed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,will I be transferred under\NLieutenant Colonel Hodgins' command?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I no longer receive any orders\Nfrom you again, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.06,0:07:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want my orders that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders are my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You no longer need to follow my orders\Nafter this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you won't have to follow\Nanyone's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Live free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that an order?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What makes you think it's an order?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.47,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really believe\Nthat I think of you as a tool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,\Nthen I wouldn't have taken you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have kept you by my side\Nall this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You should realize this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm upset...\NThis pain is because I--!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You have feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.91,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a heart, just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then why are you reacting that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're capable of expressions!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're scared of me right now, aren't you?\NYou don't like being yelled at, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're angry that I'm being unfair to you,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-I don't know!\N-Stop lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I only want to keep getting orders\Nfrom you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I have your orders, I can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.63,0:09:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's painful for me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to see that you view yourself as a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm the one\Nthat made you this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You still put your trust in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be battling in a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about this next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't write it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I have feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I had them, even back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I don't know what...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what you want\Nto say to the major?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The deadline is tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you write it by tomorrow morning,\NI'll take it to the office myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You should write one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's something short.\NEven if it's just one sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a Mr. Bougainvillea\Nhere to see Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been busy writing\Nall of those letters for the air show.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.83,0:11:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to be the one\Nto drag you away on your day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.75,0:11:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you've been\Nto our mansion in Leiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just mention this\Nso you won't be surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but her memory is a little fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.98,0:11:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The one you wanted to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The one he wanted us to take in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally came.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.46,0:12:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.34,0:12:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Gilbert not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother, Gilbert is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.89,0:12:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He is with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same color as his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the same color as your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not know the word,\Nso, I never said it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But your eyes were beautiful\Nfrom the moment we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And, so, what was your\Nrelationship with Gilbert?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The major took me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:12:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,raised me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and employed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.24,0:13:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He passed away at the Battle of Intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. That is why you had her\Ncome here, isn't it, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not have to carry that burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Diethard told me\Nto give up on Gilbert already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though he can't do it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of them were very close\Nsince they were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My son is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I will never forget him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it may be painful,\NI will always carry him in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.65,0:14:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because even now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.57,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I still love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:14:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live to honor his memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Live.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Live a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my final order.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.12,0:15:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,no longer need orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gilbert didn't treat her\Nlike a tool like I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why even though she lost\Nboth arms and her master,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,she will never lose\Nall the important things he has given her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad the weather turned out nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time\Nsince it last snowed in Leiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Luculia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been busy\Nscribing for the air show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wrote many letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:17:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter of my own for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote one, too. To my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sure it will reach them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,To my future self! I'll be\Nthe number one Doll in Leiden then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the number one Doll on the continent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's some dream.\N-What about you, Erica?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've recently started liking someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-so, I've--\N-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-Who? Who is it!?\N-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to know\Nwhat I wrote in my letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually wrote one to Hodgins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote that I'd be the future boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you coming after my job?\NHow could you write that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk.\NYou want to share what you wrote?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.79,0:18:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,-"To Daddy's future daughter."\N-How did you get that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.50,0:18:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your trash can was filled\Nwith your rough drafts, Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,"Daddy is waiting for you to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I pray that you grow up healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That you find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That you fall in love with someone\Nwho loves you in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.32,0:18:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And that the world of your future\Nand of your future children...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is one without conflict,\Nfilled with happiness."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these people's feelings\Nare falling from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"To my beloved Major Gilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope all is well with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you are not stressed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Spring, summer, autumn, and winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Many seasons have passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am still waiting for your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I did not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not understand any of your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But I started learning about emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from this new life you have provided me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Through writing letters for others.\NThrough the people I have met.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.10,0:20:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I still believe that you are still alive\Nout there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why\NI will continue to live my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not know what lies ahead,\Nbut I will simply live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:21:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we should ever meet again,\Nthis is what I would tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.30,0:21:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I now understand what the words...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,'I love you' mean."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.73,0:22:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet! You have a new request!\NThey say it's urgent!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Benedict, go make some tea.\N-What? Why do I have to get the tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.78,0:22:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet, you have a client waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.62,0:23:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.04,0:23:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,THE AUTO MEMORY DOLL
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,THE AUTO MEMORY DOLL\NAND "I LOVE YOU"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.07,0:23:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a pleasure to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.57,0:23:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will travel anywhere\Nto meet your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Auto Memory Doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet Evergarden at your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by\NZensho Yamamoto
